<h4>Hide an album</h4>
<p>Use tag <code>&lt;!--hidden--&gt;</code> in the album name:</p>
<ul>
  <li>it won't be displayed in the parent album</li>
  <li>it remains visible in the album menu</li>
</ul>

<h4>Hide an album from the menu</h4>
<p>Use tag <code>&lt;!--mb-hidden--&gt;</code> in the album name:</p>
<ul>
  <li>it won't be displayed in the album menu</li>
  <li>it remains visible in the parent album</li>
</ul>

<h4>Hide a photo</h4>
<p>Use tag <code>&lt;!--hidden--&gt;</code> in the photo name:</p>
<ul>
  <li>it won't be displayed on the thumbnails page</li>
  <li>it remains visible inside the album</li>
</ul>